title: Hoover Refrigerator Shelf Retainer Bar End Cap
description: Hoover Refrigerator Shelf Retainer Bar End Cap ★★★★★ ★★★★★ 8 Reviews PartSelect Number PS11743131 Manufacturer Part Number WP61002112 The shelf retainer bar end cap is used to keep the retainer bar in place, and can be used on either the right or left hand side of the bar. This white, OEM end cap is approximately 2 inches long, and made entirely of plastic. The shelf bar and cap snap into place on the door to attach the door shelf bar to the inner door liner. This part is also known as a rail end cap. If the door bar is not properly attached to the inner door liner, your items will not be secure on the shelf, and are likely to fall.
